root: ^The kitchen appears cleaned, recently scrubbed down. If there were traces of evidence, they might be lost now.
^But, why would anyone clean at such a late hour? It seems a bit out of place.
^It's pretty late, and I doubt I will find the chef at this hour. I'll have to continue my inquiry tomorrow.
^Marvin Sullivan, the chef, is next on my list. I need to understand what she might know about Rachel's last moments in this kitchen.
